Setup --> Flows --> new flows --> Screen flow --> Create --> 
Create a screen flow.
Add a screen element.
    Label: My Screen
    API Name: My_Screen
    Configure Footer : select Hide Previous and Hide Pause
    Next or Finish Button : select Use the standard label.
Add a Display Text field:
    Display Text: Hello, World
    API Name: Hello_World
Save the flow:
    Flow Label: Hello World
    Flow API: Hello_World
Activate the flow.
